<item>
            <title>[PIG-1298] Restore file traversal behavior to Pig loaders</title>
                <link>https://issues.apache.org/jira/browse/PIG-1298</link>
                <project id="12310730" key="PIG">Pig</project>
                    <description>&lt;p&gt;Given a location to a Pig loader, it is expected to recursively load all the files under the location (i.e., all the files returned with  &quot;ls -R&quot; command). However, after the transition to using Hadoop 20 API,  only files returned with &quot;ls&quot; command are loaded.&lt;/p&gt;



</description>
